      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm 24 weeks pregnant and my sinus infection is getting really bad like i can barely breathe through my nose and my head hurts so much. i have some pseudoephedrine left over from before i was pregnant, is it okay to take that to help clear things up? i just really need some relief so i can sleep",
