      "content": "wait a ruptured uterus?? that sounds terrifying. are you sure? i've read online that some people say it's fine in the second trimester if you only take a little bit. i'm just so miserable and i don't want to go to the ER if it's not an emergency, it's so expensive. is there really no way to take a small dose just to get through the night?",
